  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213530/extras/a71452e078c7d0fa97406bb4cc700ac2.avif?t=1768708378\" width=610 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Those who go to their deaths salute you!</strong> In the world of gladiators, where every fight is a struggle for survival, the arena becomes a place where blood flows in rivers. Here, in the yellow circle, where there is no place for fear and weakness, gladiators fight for their life and glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features modes that allow you to test your strength in battle. In PvP mode, you can face off against other players, where every battle is a struggle for the leading position. In PvE mode you will fight against artificial intelligence to develop your skills and become even stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213530/extras/a71452e078c7d0fa97406bb4cc700ac2.avif?t=1768708378\" width=610 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Those who go to their deaths salute you!</strong> In the world of gladiators, where every fight is a struggle for survival, the arena becomes a place where blood flows in rivers. Here, in the yellow circle, where there is no place for fear and weakness, gladiators fight for their life and glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features modes that allow you to test your strength in battle. In PvP mode, you can face off against other players, where every battle is a struggle for the leading position. In PvE mode you will fight against artificial intelligence to develop your skills and become even stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
